        <Parent_String>hair by composition or origin [300011815], hair (material) [300011814], hair and hair components as materials [300192982], keratinous material [300192973], animal material [300011793], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
